title: BloodRayne (Digital Webbing)
description:
Series of comics published by Digital Webbing inspired by the video games developed by Terminal Reality.

Rayne is a bloodthirsty American dhampir, born c.1915-1916 after her mother was raped by her vampire father. After spending her teenage years trying to hunt down and kill her father she was recruited by the mysterious Brimstone Society who send her out on missions to eliminate supernatural threats to the world.

Series has been written by Steven O'Connell and Troy Wall; and illustrated by Steve Scott, Mark A. Robinson, Robert Delatorre and Chad Hardin.  Additional covers have been provided by Mark Robinson, Stacie Ponder, Greg Horn and Jeremy Roberts.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
